229	    // (sub=[]); `method/<lemma>/<N>/_` applies at the inner empty-case
230	    // sub-path (sub=[""]).  Without this distinction the click on a
231	    // post-simplify sub-case's method list would resolve to the
232	    // wrong proof node.
